{"tid":1656024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[轉發ptt] Steve Kerr & Lebron James 被網友起底","createTime":"2019-10-15T11:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:36:08.000Z","uid":147785,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a76d9a01630bc6a6c1f9ff12d8b9a268e2b395","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Z9KZJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Z9KZJO.jpg&h=c1aed69c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意指Steve Kerr 一早已經知香港發生咩事 並唔係佢自己所講咁 唔了解香港事態<br />\n<br />\n另外美國論壇《Reddit》更曾翻出他在2017年時說過的一段話：「當你綜觀世界歷史，最大的問題就是人們沉默了。」，暗諷柯爾的雙重標準。該文底下也有網友諷刺道：「但有時候你會遇到更大的問題......習近平。」<br />\n節錄自: <a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2943633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943633&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=690f1f40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2943633&h=8c3728af\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2943633</a><br />\n___________________________________________________________________<br />\nLeBron James 被人挖出曾經在馬丁路德金恩被暗殺50年冥誕那天發的文章。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyiDjJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyiDjJT.jpg&h=6d82bc2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLeBron James認為「任何地方的不公不義，都威脅著所有<br />\n地方的公平正義。當我們對重要的事變得沉默，我們人生便開始失去價值。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是2018年的推文，很明顯過往LeBron James是很願意替正義發聲的，但是到今天怎麼突<br />\n然變成是一個不應該公開討論的情形？<br />\n所以LeBron James 是為什麼認為不應該公開討論? 什麼原因讓他忘記自己身為人權鬥士<br />\n的光榮使命?」<br />\n<br />\n轉發自: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1571126837.A.937.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FNBA%2FM.1571126837.A.937.html&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=a98bb03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1571126837.A.937.html</a>"},{"pid":"cad31cb486dd78debea50b220bfa2157068463bc","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"有時個名既翻譯唔同香港<br />\n<br />\n唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2be58e7f9105d3dc568b8171e2f404356d90fd8","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"dd3cd59261b6e00e3798610c80daefbf3b771999","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"2553ad9bcaeace762f27ea2d72cd659db9f84adb","tid":1656024,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"69c92e1239435d6a36db19384afee2c4f7171c26","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"6cef2c4b64155adfbe53ecde668c4e2263223825","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"214073c1df94d79a31fb3febdd31ec3a4782b609","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"79fb8392886cdea24f9ce751dab12031c165dc79","tid":1656024,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cd3e78117c9592d422db8abc2d9c984b08fbd33e","tid":1656024,"uid":44298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"因為要舔共，公義，不了"},{"pid":"161447ce8afdfd676cca6a640b264f775f1e2a9b","tid":1656024,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"I prefer RMB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" clas